snippet.title: One Skill game trailer
snippet.description:
This is the latest game for Vircon32, where you can use 4 different skills! As always, this game and the console itself are free and open source. You can get them at the website (see link below).

🌏 Vircon32 website: https://www.vircon32.com
🐦 Twitter account: https://twitter.com/vircon32
